\c 9
\nb
\v 1 Ngoba konke lokhu ngakubeka enhliziyweni yami ukuhlolisisa konke lokhu\x + 3.18.\x*, ukuthi abalungileyo labahlakaniphileyo lezenzo zabo kusesandleni sikaNkulunkulu\x + 8.14.\x*; loba uthando kumbe inzondo, kakho umuntu okwaziyo, konke okuphambi kwabo\x + Heb. 12.5-7.\x*.
\v 2 Konke \add kwehla\add* ngokufananayo kubo bonke\x + Jobe 9.22. 21.7-18. Hlab. 73.3,12,13. Mal. 3.14,15.\x*; sinye isehlakalo kolungileyo lakomubi, komuhle, lakohlambulukileyo lakongahlambulukanga, lakonikela umhlatshelo lakonganikeli umhlatshelo\x + 2.14.\x*; njengolungileyo sinjalo isoni, ofungayo njengowesaba isifungo\x + Zek. 5.3. Mal. 3.5.\x*.
\v 3 Yilobu ububi phakathi kwakho konke okwenziwa ngaphansi kwelanga, ukuthi sinye isehlakalo kukho konke\x + 2.14.\x*, futhi lenhliziyo yabantwana babantu igcwele ububi, lobuhlanya busenhliziyweni yabo besaphila, lemva kwalokhu \add baya\add* kwabafileyo\x + 1.17.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Ngoba kulowo ohlanganiswe labo bonke abaphilayo kulethemba, ngoba inja ephilayo ingcono kulesilwane esifileyo.
\v 5 Ngoba abaphilayo bayazi ukuthi bazakufa, kodwa abafileyo kabazi lutho, njalo kabaselawo umvuzo\x + Jobe 14.21. Isa. 63.16.\x*, ngoba ukukhunjulwa kwabo sekukhohlakele\x + 8.10. Hlab. 31.12. Isa. 26.14. Hlab. 88.5,12. Jobe 7.8-10.\x*.
\v 6 Futhi uthando lwabo lenzondo yabo lomona wabo sekubhubhile, njalo kabasayikuba lesabelo laphakade kukho konke okwenziwayo ngaphansi kwelanga\x + 1.10.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Hamba, udle ukudla kwakho ngentokozo, unathe iwayini lakho ngenhliziyo elenjabulo\x + 2.24. 1 Sam. 1.18.\x*, ngoba uNkulunkulu\x + 9.11. 11.9.\x* usethokozile ngemisebenzi yakho\x + 1.10.\x*.
\v 8 Izigqoko zakho kazibe ngezimhlophe ngesikhathi sonke\x + Isam. 3.4.\x*, lamafutha angasweleki ekhanda lakho\x + Hlab. 23.5.\x*.
\v 9 Kholisa impilo lomkakho omthandayo zonke izinsuku zempilo yakho eyize akunike yona ngaphansi kwelanga, zonke izinsuku zakho eziyize\x + 3.13.\x*, ngoba lesi yisabelo sakho empilweni, lemtshikatshikeni owutshikatshika ngaphansi kwelanga\x + 2.10. 2.24.\x*.
\v 10 Loba kuyini isandla sakho esikutholayo ukukwenza\x + Hlu. 9.33.\x* kwenze ngamandla akho\x + Roma 12.11.\x*, ngoba kawukho umsebenzi lecebo lolwazi lenhlakanipho engcwabeni lapho oya khona\x + 7.25.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Ngaphenduka ngabona ngaphansi kwelanga\x + 4.1,7. 9.7-10.\x* ukuthi umjaho kawusiwabalejubane\x + Amos 2.14,15.\x*, lempi kayisiyamaqhawe, futhi lesinkwa kasisabahlakaniphileyo\x + 2 Lan. 20.15. Jer. 9.23.\x*, futhi lenotho kayisiyabalolwazi, futhi lomusa kawusiwezingcitshi\x + Zaga 13.15.\x*, kodwa isikhathi lesehlakalo\x + 1 Kho. 5.4.\x* kwehlela bonke\x + 2.14.\x*.
\v 12 Ngoba futhi umuntu kasazi isikhathi sakhe\x + 8.7.\x*; njengenhlanzi ezibanjwa embuleni elibi\x + Zaga 12.12.\x*, lanjengezinyoni ezibanjwa emjibileni\x + Zaga 7.23.\x*, njengazo abantwana babantu bayabanjwa esikhathini esibi, lapho sibajuma\x + Zaga 29.6. Luka 21.35.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Lale inhlakanipho ngayibona ngaphansi kwelanga, njalo yaba nkulu kimi.
\v 14 Kwakukhona umuzi omncinyane, okwakulabantu abalutshwana phakathi kwawo; kwasekusiza inkosi enkulu kuwo, yawuvimbezela\x + Luka 19.43.\x*, yawakhela amadundulu amakhulu okuvimbezela\x + Zaga 12.12.\x*.
\v 15 Kwasekutholakala phakathi kwawo umuntu ohlakaniphileyo ongumyanga\x + 4.13.\x*, yena-ke ngenhlakanipho yakhe wawukhulula lowomuzi\x + 2 Sam. 20.22.\x*. Kanti kakho owake wamkhumbula lowomuntu ongumyanga\x + 4.13.\x*.
\v 16 Mina ngasengisithi: Inhlakanipho ingcono kulamandla\x + 7.19.\x*, lanxa ukuhlakanipha komyanga kuseyiswa\x + Mark. 6.2,3.\x*\x + 4.13.\x* lamazwi akhe engalalelwa.
\v 17 Amazwi abahlakaniphileyo azwiwa ekupholeni ngcono kulokumemeza kobusayo phakathi kwezithutha\x + 4.6.\x*.
\v 18 Inhlakanipho ingcono kulezikhali zempi\x + 7.19.\x*, kodwa isoni esisodwa sichitha ubuhle obunengi\x + Josh. 7.1,11,12.\x*.